{"article_id":"Q3fi7XE121Xj8pKB","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Roger Stone , a longtime adviser to Donald Trump , has said","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"he will not testify against the president","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"after he was arrested by the FBI on Friday morning","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and indicted on seven criminal charges .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"Stone , a veteran Republican operative , appeared in federal court in Fort Lauderdale","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"charged by special counsel Robert Mueller with obstruction , lying to Congress and witness tampering .","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"He was released on $ 250,000 bail","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"and denies wrongdoing .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"Mueller alleged in a long-anticipated indictment","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"that Stone , 66 , was asked by Trump ' s 2016 presidential campaign to get inside information about emails","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"that were stolen from Democrats by Russian government hackers","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"and passed to WikiLeaks .","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"A senior campaign official \" was directed \" to tell Stone to find out what damaging information WikiLeaks had about Hillary Clinton","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"even after it was reported that the material","depth":11},{"id":14,"text":"being published by the group","depth":11},{"id":15,"text":"came from Russia ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"the indictment said .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"The allegations were the first","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"to connect Trump ' s campaign to the explosive release of the emails","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"stolen by Russian operatives .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Their release disrupted Clinton ' s campaign","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"and led the Democratic party ' s chairwoman to resign .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"US intelligence agencies have concluded","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"that Russia ' s interference was aimed at damaging Clinton ' s campaign","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"and helping Trump .","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"Mueller is investigating","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"whether any Trump associates coordinated with the Russian effort .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Appearing outside the federal courthouse in Fort Lauderdale after his hearing ,","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"Stone smiled","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"he would resist pressure from Mueller","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"to turn on Trump .","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"\" I will not testify against the president","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"because I would have to bear false witness , \"","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"The White House press secretary , Sarah Sanders , repeatedly declined to say","depth":4},{"id":36,"text":"if the order for Stone was given by Trump himself .","depth":4},{"id":37,"text":"Sanders claimed","depth":4},{"id":38,"text":"the charges against Stone , an early adviser to Trump ' s campaign , had \" nothing to do with the president \" .","depth":4},{"id":39,"text":"Roger Stone 's arrest may renew threat of impeachment for Trump","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"Read more","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"But Dianne Feinstein , a senior Democratic senator , noted","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"that the phrase \" Trump campaign \" appeared 24 times in Stone ' s indictment .","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"\" It ' s time for President Trump and his top aides to be truthful with the American people , \"","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Feinstein said .","depth":6},{"id":45,"text":"Mark Warner , the Democratic vice-chairman of the Senate intelligence committee , said","depth":5},{"id":46,"text":"the new charges showed","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"Stone ' s activities \" happened at least with the full knowledge of ,","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"and appear to have been encouraged by ,","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"the highest levels of the Trump campaign \" .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Stone shuffled into court at 11am","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"shackled at the waist and hands .","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"Dressed in a blue polo shirt and jeans ,","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"he appeared disheveled after his 6am wake-up call from the FBI .","depth":6},{"id":54,"text":"Protesters gathered outside the courthouse in downtown Fort Lauderdale ,","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"some booing","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"and waving \" Impeach Trump \" placards .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"The indictment ,","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"which was issued in Washington DC ,","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"alleged","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that in June or July 2016 , Stone told senior Trump campaign officials","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"that he knew","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"WikiLeaks had damaging information on Clinton .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Julian Assange , the head of WikiLeaks , first publicly hinted","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"that the group had information","depth":12},{"id":65,"text":"to release on Clinton","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"on 12 June , in an interview on British television .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Two days later it was first reported that Russia had hacked Democratic computer systems .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Mueller said","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"after WikiLeaks began publishing the first leaked Democratic emails on 22 July ,","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"Stone repeatedly attempted to get to WikiLeaks through intermediaries ,","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"and then \" told the Trump campaign about potential future releases of damaging material \" .","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"First he sent emails","depth":12},{"id":74,"text":"urging Jerome Corsi , a rightwing commentator , to get their mutual friend Ted Malloch , a London-based academic , to visit Assange at Ecuador ' s embassy in London ,","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"where Assange has been holed up for more than six years .","depth":13},{"id":76,"text":"Corsi sent back what he said","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"was inside information .","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"Then Stone began messaging with Randy Credico , a friend and eccentric radio host","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"who had his own connections to WikiLeaks .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Mueller said","depth":12},{"id":81,"text":"that on 1 October 2016 , Credico told Stone","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"that there would be \" big news \" from WikiLeaks later that week .","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"\" Now pretend you don ' t know me ...","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"Hillary ' s campaign will die this week , \"","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"On 7 October , WikiLeaks began publishing emails","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"stolen from John Podesta , the chairman of Clinton ' s campaign .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Mueller said on Friday","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"that soon after the first Podesta emails were published ,","depth":13},{"id":90,"text":"an associate of Trump ' s campaign boss Steve Bannon sent a text message to Stone","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"that said :","depth":15},{"id":92,"text":"\" Well done. \"","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"Stone took credit","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"for passing on inside information in later talks with senior Trump campaign staff ,","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"Mueller said .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"Although Stone did not hold an official position for much of Trump ' s 2016 campaign ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"he is perhaps the president ' s longest-serving informal political adviser ,","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"stemming from a close association in New York","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"spanning more than a decade .","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"Stone has attracted intense scrutiny from Mueller and other investigators ,","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"after a tweet and other public statements","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"he made in the summer of 2016","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"indicated","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"that he had knowledge","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"the emails","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"stolen from Podesta","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"would soon be released .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"Late last year he predicted","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"he would be indicted .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"\" Robert Mueller is coming for me , \"","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"Stone wrote to supporters in August .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"Stone denied wrongdoing","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"and said","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"he faced legal peril","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"simply because he had advised Trump for several decades .","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"A self-proclaimed \" dirty trickster \" , Stone has been a controversial figure in Republican political circles","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"stretching back to the 1970s ,","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"when he worked on Richard Nixon ' s notorious committee for re-election .","depth":8},{"id":119,"text":"He has a tattoo of Nixon ' s face on his back .","depth":6},{"id":120,"text":"The indictment also said","depth":7},{"id":121,"text":"Stone made false statements","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"when questioned by the intelligence committee of the House of Representatives .","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"When asked","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"if he had no emails or other communications","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"relating to WikiLeaks and the hacked Democratic documents ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"Stone allegedly said :","depth":9},{"id":127,"text":"\" That is correct .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"Not to my knowledge . \"","depth":10},{"id":129,"text":"In fact ,","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"the indictment said ,","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"Stone \" sent and received numerous emails and text messages during the 2016 campaign","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"in which he discussed \" WikiLeaks , Assange , and their possession of hacked emails .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"It was Stone who first recommended","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"that Trump ' s team hire as its campaign manager Paul Manafort , his former business partner .","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Manafort has since been found guilty on eight counts of financial crimes","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"and is said to have breached a plea agreement with the special counsel .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"Manafort made his first court appearance in months on Friday","depth":8},{"id":138,"text":"as prosecutors and defence lawyers argue over whether he intentionally lied to investigators .","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"Mueller ' s team say","depth":9},{"id":140,"text":"Manafort repeatedly lied to them","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"even after he began cooperating last September .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Manafort ' s lawyers say","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"he simply forgot some details .","depth":9}],"relations":[{"parent":287,"left":182,"right":286,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":178,"right":181,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":170,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":170,"left":151,"right":169,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":151,"left":147,"right":150,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":147,"left":145,"right":146,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":145,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":146,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":150,"left":148,"right":149,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":148,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":169,"left":164,"right":168,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":159,"right":163,"relation":"e